      "text": "Receiver\n   │\n   │ publishes stealth keys\n   ▼\nBackend\n   │\n   │ derive one-time address\n   ▼\nSender\n   │\n   │ send transaction\n   ▼\nBitGo Wallet\n   │\n   │ transaction on blockchain\n   ▼\nReceiver scans using view key",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
